22:
Phew... Looks like that was the last of
them.
28:
A-Alk! I-I can't hear them! The
sprites! Their voices are gone!
50:
Or at least, it will be... Anyway, we
should focus on finding shelter.
58:
I-I'm sure I'll hear their voices again
in no time... This is just a temporary
affliction...
66:
I am... but a worm. A useless and
insignificant wooorm...
70:
C-come on, cheer up... It's not that
bad, right?
74:
It very much is! My powers have yet
to return, and now I have not only
stranded myself here, but you as
well!
78:
And I was not able to offer you any
assistance at all! You did everything
from lighting this fire to foraging
food and water!
82:
Don't be so hard on yourself. I took
care of that stuff 'cause I already
know how to do it.
84:
Can't really fulfill Guild requests if I
don't know how to survive in the
wilderness.
88:
Urgh... I was able to do all those
tasks and more back in my own
village!
91:
How did I never realize how useless I
am without the sprites?! I... Heh...
95:
Heh... Hnngh... I am the world's
greatest fooru... Queen of all trashu...
No wonder the sprites abandoned
me...
100:
...Well, I don't think you're either of
those things.
108:
Ah, sorry. That probably doesn't
mean much coming from someone
outside your village, but still...
112:
Oh, looks like the fish is done. Want
some?
116:
I... cannot accept this meal. I have
done nothing to earn it.
121:
Well, consider this a loan for
tomorrow. You're not gonna be able
to do much on an empty stomach.
124:
Besides, I'm sure the sick still get
meals in your village, don't they?
138:
We'll rest up tonight and then
explore the island more tomorrow.
140:
Who knows? Maybe we'll find people
living here.
144:
But... what will we do if we find no
one?
148:
Well... I guess we'll have to wait for
help or make a boat on our own.
152:
...Understood. In the worst case
scenario, should we find ourselves
living on this island for the rest of our
lives...
156:
I shall work hard to ensure that your
descendants populate this island for
generations to come!
166:
Though the sprites have forsaken
me, I hope you will accept this fooru
worm!
170:
H-hold on, it's not like we're that far
from Paradise Isle anyway.
173:
I'm sure the others will find us
sooner rather than later.
194:
Do you think your powers have
returned?
215:
D-don't give up! You still felt
something just now, right? That's
progress!
219:
Y-you're right... This is better than
nothing!
